//    before the backend's own Create/Update. Returns Allow or Deny
//    with a reason string; the component server turns a Deny into
//    an HTTP 400/422 that propagates the backend's reason verbatim
//    to the client.
//
//  - Mutate(MutateRequest) -> MutateResponse
